media/**
# Bundle ONLY the extension icon: it is read straight from the .vsix via
# package.json "icon". README screenshots are deliberately NOT packaged —
# vsce rewrites the README's relative `media/...` paths to absolute GitHub
# raw URLs at package time (verified: `media/...` →
# `https://github.com/deyuf/urdf-studio/raw/HEAD/media/...`), so the
# Marketplace page and the in-editor README fetch them remotely. The image
# files stay in the repo (those URLs resolve against the default branch);
# they just no longer bloat the .vsix with a multi-MB hero gif.
!media/icon.png
